---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Social Proof for Senior Care Agencies — Build Family Trust | SocialProof" description="Help families choose your senior care agency with confidence. SocialProof helps home care and senior care businesses collect and display testimonials. Free to start." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/senior-care">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: .9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
    .trust-bar { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: #f8fafc; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    section { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .benefit-card { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .benefit-card .icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .quote-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .quote-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .quote-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 1rem; font-style: italic; }
    .quote-author { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; }
    .quote-role { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #888; }
    .stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
    .steps { counter-reset: step; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .15rem; }
    .step h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .35rem; }
    .step p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .cta-block { text-align: center; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .cta-block h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .cta-block p { color: #bfdbfe; max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .cta-block .cta-btn { background: #fff; color: #2563eb; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for/">Industries</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>Social proof for senior care agencies — earn the trust of worried families</h1>
  <p>Families searching for home care or assisted living do exhaustive research before choosing. Testimonials from other families on your website make that decision easier and faster. Free to start.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Start free today →</a>
</div>

<div class="trust-bar">
  <span>💛 Built for home care agencies</span>
  <span>✓ Family-friendly testimonial collection</span>
  <span>✓ Works on any website</span>
  <span>✓ 5-minute setup</span>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Why social proof is critical for senior care agencies</h2>
  <div class="benefits-grid">
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
      <h3>Families are making the hardest decision of their lives</h3>
      <p>Choosing care for a parent or loved one is emotionally charged and terrifying. Reading stories from families who've been through it — and found peace of mind — is the most powerful thing you can show them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">🔍</div>
      <h3>Online research drives care decisions</h3>
      <p>Adult children researching options for aging parents spend hours online before making contact. Your website is your first impression — make it count with authentic family testimonials.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">🤝</div>
      <h3>Differentiate on care quality, not just price</h3>
      <p>Most agencies look the same on paper. Testimonials from real families describing specific caregivers, specific moments, and real outcomes tell a story no brochure can match.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">📞</div>
      <h3>Convert website visitors into inquiry calls</h3>
      <p>Families researching senior care are often overwhelmed and hesitant to reach out. A wall of warm, specific testimonials gives them the confidence to pick up the phone.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:#f8fafc; margin:0; padding: 3rem 2rem; max-width:100%;">
  <div style="max-width:880px; margin:0 auto;">
    <h2>What your widget could look like</h2>
    <div class="quote-grid">
      <div class="quote-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="quote-text">"When my mother's dementia progressed, we were devastated and didn't know where to turn. The care team here felt like extended family from day one. Mom is happy and safe — that's everything."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">Catherine M.</div>
        <div class="quote-role">Daughter of home care client</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="quote-text">"We interviewed four agencies before choosing this one. The caregivers are thoughtful, reliable, and genuinely kind. Dad looks forward to his visits. We've never once regretted our choice."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">Robert T.</div>
        <div class="quote-role">Son of care recipient</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="quote-text">"The coordination was seamless after my husband's surgery. Every caregiver showed up on time, knew his needs, and communicated clearly with us. It made an impossible situation manageable."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">Linda W.</div>
        <div class="quote-role">Spouse of post-surgical care client</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Simple setup, powerful results</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Create your free account</h3>
        <p>Sign up with your email. No credit card, no trial period. Your account includes one testimonial widget with unlimited submissions, forever.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Send your collection link to families</h3>
        <p>Share your unique link via email, text, or your care coordination portal. Families can submit a testimonial in about 2 minutes — just their name and their story.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Review and approve before publishing</h3>
        <p>You control what appears on your widget. Review every submission and only publish the testimonials that represent your agency's values.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Embed on your agency website</h3>
        <p>Paste one line of code into your website. Works with WordPress, Squarespace, Wix, Webflow, and any custom-built site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="cta-block">
    <h2>Give families the reassurance they need to choose you</h2>
    <p>Free forever for 1 widget. Setup takes 5 minutes. No tech skills required.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Create your free account →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/for/" style="color:#999">All industries</a> · <a href="/pricing" style="color:#999">Pricing</a> · <a href="/privacy" style="color:#999">Privacy</a></p>
</footer>
</Base>
